Manage Your Groups and Contacts
Add connections, and manage your contacts with the ease of instant messaging.


Group and Industry Broadcasts
Listen to internal updates or TV audio broadcasts. 


Shortcuts
Use shortcuts to simplify the way you work. 


Alerts and Notifications
Pop-ups signify incoming calls and messages. 






















