Who We Are
Cloud9 was established in 2014 by a group of motivated entrepreneurs who individually helped build and pioneer trader communication technology. At Cloud9 they joined forces to reinvent the way traders interact with their counterparties and middle and back office staff.  Today, we’re transforming communication both on and off of the trading floor with modern, cloud-based communication technology in more than 34 countries.
Our mission is to eliminate the complexity and hassle of dealing with traditional telephony solutions while delivering services that are inherently more reliable, less expensive and of higher quality across enterprises.
































