C9 Trader at a Glance




Reduce your communications costs by up to 50% by eliminating expensive private lines and desktop hardware.




Scale up or scale down your number of users based on your business needs. 





Instantly find existing counterparties via our global community of users, or make connections to new counterparties.




Integrated recording supports mobility and provides added compliance.  Activity is also tracked by user to provide enhanced reporting.





Unified Communications and Collaboration integration with major voice service providers, Cisco Call Manager and Skype for Business enables you to leverage existing enterprise communication capabilities.




Ensure voice data and recordings are secure in transit and at rest with triple encryption technology.





Manage your users globally via the Cloud9 portal to eliminate the hassle of managing multiple, disparate systems by location or geography.




Cloud9 also supports dial-tone, private lines, hoots, audio broadcasts, ambient speakers, group call capabilities, and all of the features traders and the back and middle office expect.










End-to-End Security

Cloud9 employs a multi-level security approach to prevent, monitor, and rapidly respond to security challenges.



























Prevention, Monitoring, Response
Cloud9 follows Information Security Management System (ISMS) guidelines from ISO 27001.  The system also employs extensive monitoring, with polices around escalation and response.













Perimeter and Network Security
Perimeter data flows and device access are identified and secured.  All network traffic is encrypted using the most secure keys and protocols, with routine 3rd party vulnerability reviews.























Server Security
Servers are configured with only necessary processes to minimize attack surfaces.  Security patches and best practices are regularly applied to running processes.













Application Security and Data Security
Cloud9 uses multifactor identification, and third party application level reviews are routinely conducted.  Data is encrypted at rest, backed up regularly, and access is isolated.



































